Protective Life Corp., the
Birmingham, Alabama-based insurer, named Michael Temple as chief
risk officer, effective Dec. 3.  Temple, who previously was risk chief at insurer  Unum
Group (UNM) , will report to Chief Executive Officer John D. Johns,
Protective said today in a statement distributed by  Business
Wire .  To contact the reporter on this story:
